data.eml:eml: The millipede tribe Sundaninini in Vietnam (Diplopoda: Polydesmida: Paradoxosomatidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Nguyen, Anh D. (2010): The millipede tribe Sundaninini in Vietnam (Diplopoda: Polydesmida: Paradoxosomatidae). Zootaxa 2479: 59-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.195376
